---
// BeliefUpdateSection.astro - False belief / belief updating section
---

<section id="belief-update" class="content-section alt-background">
  <div class="section-container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Belief Revision Task</h2>
    <p class="section-description">
      We introduce a dynamic perturbation task to probe the agent's ability to handle non-stationarity.
      After exploration, 4 objects are secretly relocated/reoriented. The agent must re-explore to identify changes.
    </p>
    
    <div class="metrics-explanation">
      <ul class="metrics-list">
        <li><strong>Identification Accuracy:</strong> F1 score for correctly identifying which objects changed.</li>
        <li><strong>Average Steps:</strong> Cost of belief revision. Includes <em>Redundancy</em> (steps taken after finding all changes).</li>
        <li><strong>Belief Correctness:</strong> Map accuracy on the changed objects.</li>
        <li><strong>Belief Inertia:</strong> Measures if the agent overwrites its old map (high score) or exhibits belief inertia (low score).</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="table-wrapper">
      <table class="probing-table">
        <thead>
          <!-- Row 1: Group Headers -->
          <tr>
            <th rowspan="2" class="model-header">Methods</th>
            <th colspan="2" class="group-header">Avg. Steps &darr;</th>
            <th colspan="2" class="group-header">Identification (%) &uarr;</th>
            <th colspan="2" class="group-header">Belief Correctness (%) &uarr;</th>
            <th colspan="2" class="group-header">Belief Inertia (%) &darr;</th>
          </tr>
          <!-- Row 2: Sub-headers -->
          <tr>
            <th class="sub-header">All</th>
            <th class="sub-header">Red.</th>
            <th class="sub-header">Ori.</th>
            <th class="sub-header">Pos.</th>
            <th class="sub-header">Ori.</th>
            <th class="sub-header">Pos.</th>
            <th class="sub-header">Ori.</th>
            <th class="sub-header">Pos.</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <!-- Vision-based World -->
          <tr class="section-row">
            <td colspan="9">Vision-based World</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="proprietary-row">
            <td class="model-name">GPT-5.2</td>
            <td>13.06</td>
            <td>6.20</td>
            <td>14.3</td>
            <td>68.0</td>
            <td>16.7</td>
            <td>42.9</td>
            <td>68.9</td>
            <td>34.7</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="proprietary-row">
            <td class="model-name">GEMINI-3 PRO</td>
            <td class="best-score">10.29</td>
            <td class="best-score">3.23</td>
            <td class="best-score">23.9</td>
            <td class="best-score">82.5</td>
            <td class="best-score">30.3</td>
            <td class="best-score">63.1</td>
            <td class="best-score">51.1</td>
            <td class="best-score">14.4</td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Text-based World -->
          <tr class="section-row">
            <td colspan="9">Text-based World</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="proprietary-row">
            <td class="model-name">GPT-5.2</td>
            <td class="best-score">6.92</td>
            <td>0.55</td>
            <td>97.9</td>
            <td>98.4</td>
            <td>89.5</td>
            <td>69.7</td>
            <td class="best-score">5.5</td>
            <td>12.5</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="proprietary-row">
            <td class="model-name">GEMINI-3 PRO</td>
            <td>7.79</td>
            <td class="best-score">0.18</td>
            <td class="best-score">98.7</td>
            <td class="best-score">98.8</td>
            <td class="best-score">91.8</td>
            <td class="best-score">72.9</td>
            <td>7.9</td>
            <td class="best-score">5.7</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <!-- Conclusion -->
    <div class="results-analysis-single" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <h3 class="analysis-heading">Belief Revision Conclusion</h3>
      <div class="findings-grid">
        <div class="finding-item">
          <span class="finding-icon">ðŸ”„</span>
          <div class="finding-content">
            <strong>Severe Belief Inertia in Vision</strong>
            <span class="finding-detail">Vision agents fail to overwrite obsolete orientation beliefs despite new evidence (Belief Inertia score ~20%).</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="finding-item">
          <span class="finding-icon">ðŸ›‘</span>
          <div class="finding-content">
            <strong>High Redundancy</strong>
            <span class="finding-detail">Vision agents take many redundant steps after changes are visible, indicating failure to recognize the revision is complete.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #belief-update .section-container {
    max-width: 1000px;
  }

  /* Metrics Explanation */
  .metrics-explanation {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }

  .metrics-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .metrics-list li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #4b5563;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .metrics-list li strong {
    color: #2a2f6c;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Table Styles (Reuse where possible, but scoped) */
  .table-wrapper {
    overflow-x: auto;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    background: white;
  }

  .probing-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  th {
    padding: 0.6rem 0.4rem;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  td {
    padding: 0.5rem 0.3rem;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .model-header {
    text-align: left;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    font-weight: 700;
    min-width: 150px;
    color: #333;
  }

  .group-header {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #2a2f6c;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .sub-header {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    background: #f0f4ff;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #555;
  }

  .section-row td {
    background: #eef2f6;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: left;
    padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
    color: #2a2f6c;
    border-top: 2px solid #dde1e6;
  }

  .model-name {
    text-align: left;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #333;
  }

  .proprietary-row {
    background-color: #FFF4F0;
  }

  .best-score {
    background-color: rgba(100, 100, 100, 0.25);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Conclusion */
  .results-analysis-single {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  }

  .analysis-heading {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #2a2f6c;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .findings-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .finding-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 3px solid #2a2f6c;
  }

  .finding-icon {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .finding-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .finding-content strong {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #1f2a60;
  }

  .finding-detail {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .findings-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>